      <title>收入差距问题推动反对派赢得立陶宛大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/income-gap-concern-drive-opposition-win-in-lithuania-s-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛社会民主党赢得 12 年来的首次议会选举，选民转向反对党，希望该党能缩小波罗的海国家日益扩大的经济差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/income-gap-concern-drive-opposition-win-in-lithuania-s-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 04:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
