      <title>澳大利亚总理所属政党在民意调查中首次落后于反对党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/australian-pm-s-party-trails-opposition-for-first-time-in-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯领导的工党在一项备受关注的投票意向民意调查中落后于中右翼反对党，凸显出定于 5 月举行的选举前竞争激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/australian-pm-s-party-trails-opposition-for-first-time-in-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 00:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
